data.name: Student Money Saver
data.description: Actively rewards our youngest members with a bonus interest rate, once the minimum $5 monthly deposit is made and no more than one withdrawal in the same month

features.additionalInfo: 24/7 online, mobile and phone banking access for Members aged 13 years and over. View only access is available for Members under 13 years
Bonus Interest is paid when at least $5 is deposited into the account for that calendar month and no more than one withdrawal is made in the same month

fees.name: Other Service Fees
fees.additionalInfo: Refer to our Fees and Charges brochure for information on other transactions which may attract fees and charges

depositRates.additionalValue: To achieve the bonus rate of interest you must deposit at least $5 in a calendar month and make no more than one withdrawal in the same month.
